## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="bd981-1085"><xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空间中集合的默认实现是不同步的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd981-1085">Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="bd981-1086">枚举整个集合本质上不是一个线程安全的过程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd981-1086">Enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="bd981-1087">若要确保枚举过程中的线程安全性，可以在整个枚举过程中锁定集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd981-1087">To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="bd981-1088">若要允许多个线程访问集合以进行读写操作，则必须实现自己的同步。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd981-1088">To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="bd981-1089"><xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> 返回一个对象，可用于同步对<xref:System.Collections.ICollection>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd981-1089"><xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> returns an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bd981-1090">同步是所有线程访问集合之前都锁定此对象时才有效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd981-1090">Synchronization is effective only if all threads lock this object before accessing the collection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bd981-1091">下面的代码演示如何使用<xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A>属性C#， C++，和 Visual Basic。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd981-1091">The following code shows the use of the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> property for C#, C++, and Visual Basic.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
ICollection ic = ...;  
lock (ic.SyncRoot)   
{  
    // Access the collection.  
}  
```  
  
```vb  
Dim ic As ICollection = ...  
SyncLock ic.SyncRoot  
    ' Access the collection.  
End SyncLock  
```  
  
```cpp#  
ICollection^ ic = ...;  
try   
{  
    Monitor::Enter(ic->SyncRoot);  
    // Access the collection.  
}  
finally   
{  
    Monitor::Exit(ic->SyncRoot);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="bd981-1092">检索此属性的值的运算复杂度为 O(1)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd981-1092">Retrieving the value of this property is an O(1) operation.</span></span>
